Jamaipanese[報載](http://www.jamaipanese.com/coracoes-sujos-post-wwii-japanese-
in-brazil/ "http://www.jamaipanese.com/coracoes-sujos-post-wwii-japanese-in-
brazil/")巴西導演文森特．阿莫林（Vicente Amorim）將於明年推出新片《污穢心靈》。

電影探討日本二戰戰敗後，巴西一件少有人知的衝突[導致當時日裔移民的分化](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2008/12/20/japan-
brazil-a-centenary-of-japanese-immigration-to-brazil/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2008/12/20/japan-brazil-a-centenary-of-
japanese-immigration-to-brazil/")。

文章裡附有葡文版電影預告片。

